Marinier Scott Brody is Amerikaanse Soldaat die meer dan 9 jaar vermist
was en waarvan werd verondersteld dat hij dood zou zijn. Homeland verteld

verbonden is aan Al Qaida. Wat we zien hoeft niet noodzakelijkerwijs er te

Leugens en nog meer leugens om toch achter de waarheid te komen. Is Brody
overgelopen? Wat schuilt er achter? Wie is de slechterik?

Storyline

Carrie Mathison, a CIA operations officer, is on probation after carrying out an unauthorized operation in Iraq. 
As a result, she has been reassigned to the Counter terrorism center. 
Whilst in Iraq, she was warned that an American prisoner had been turned by Al-Qaeda. When Nicholas Brody, a U.S. Marine Sergeant, 
is rescued after being held hostage since 2003, she suspects that he is the turned American prisoner. 
Brody is received home as a war hero, so Carrie goes to any lengths possible, ignoring protocol, to catch him out.
